{
  "stem": "27150.8",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we-- that means that was a freighter with not enough drinking water, you see, or very little.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so we had to take special soap, you see, to-- that's in order to use sea water.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And most of the time we spent on the deck.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I told you before, you see, that means I lost-- one of my last serpents went through the mouth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And you see, we had a fellow with a-- an accordion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we were singing and listening and watching the dolphins and--",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The journey lasted about 20 days.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very slowly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nowhere.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stopped in Sydney.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We arrived in Sydney on the 15th, and we were picked up by the Jewish community, and we were taken to a party, which was sort of strange to us.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That means there was a buffet ready, and the hostess made-- bang, bang, bang-- and everybody just went to the tables.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said-- we thought, it's a hungry nation, you see, by chasing the food.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But we were showed Sydney.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And between Sydney and Melbourne, we already travelled, you see, the passenger class, because every freighter has 12 berth for passengers which, on the way from Hong Kong, were occupied by pregnant women and-- and some people who booked.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, while in Sydney, we got familiar with Australian fruit, with everything, and after the American, everything seemed cheap, very cheap.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we didn't know yet how-- how were the Australian wages.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Listen, in my first impression, what I've been looking for is a WC, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] you see.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "After that, I started looking around, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] you see, to find something-- the fellow who brought us to Australia--",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kupercyn, Stan Kupercyn.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-U-P-E-R-C-Y-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
